name: Attack
note:
Skill #1 will be used when you select
the Attack command.

name: Guard
note:

description:
Throw your equipped ball full-force, dealing damage
to multiple enemies with the ricochet.
name: Throw Ball

description:
Fire your shotgun with a bigger gauge round. Hits
harder, but has a large damage variance.
name: Spread Shot

description:
Fire a bolt of electricity.
Deals a small amount of ELECTRO damage.
name: Static Jolt

description:
Creates a barrier of electricity. Blocks damage 
and sometimes counters attacks with ELECTRO damage.
name: Volt Guard

description:
Slide forward, leaving sparks in your wake.
GROUNDS enemies and deals ELECTRO damage.
name: Shocking Slide

description:
A massive thunderbolt that shreds the landscape.
Deals ELECTRO damage to all foes.
name: Lightning Crash

description:
Chug a bottle of iced coffee.
Maxes SKILL and boosts SPEED next turn only.
name: Drink Ice Coffee

description:
Massively grow in strength!
Boosts ATK and HP REGEN for a few turns.
name: Roid Up!

description:
Smash an enemy for massive damage! Deals damage to 1 
enemy (MORE VS MARK) and gains SKILL. Always hits last.
name: Shattering Blow

description:
Pummel an enemy with multiple rapid strikes!
Hits an enemy for KINETIC damage 6 times.
name: Beatdown

description:
Shatter an enemy's jaw, dealing damage and leaving them
vulnerable. Deals KINETIC damage and reduces DEFENSE.
name: Jawbreaker

description:
Bolster your defenses and rapidly heal. 
Taking damage ends this effect.
name: Lockdown

description:
Scare all enemies, causing them to quake in fear.
Enemies will attack your allies instead of you.
name: Terrify

description:
Harasses an enemy until they surrender.
Skip an enemy's move.
name: Shatter Will

description:
Spin around rapidly, hitting multiple enemies.
Deals damage to 3 random targets (MORE VS MARK).
name: Spin Slash

description:
Find an enemy's weak spot, allowing some attacks to hit
a lot harder. MARKs enemies.
name: Weakpoint Found

description:
Damage an enemy, then expose their critical points,
causing all players to crit more often.
name: Sonar Arrow

description:
Enter a trance state of pure combat power, allowing you
to take multiple actions and regenerate SKILL.
name: Hunter's Trance

description:
Give an ally a Chill Pill, causing them to deal CRYO
damage, and increasing their ATTACK for a few turns.
name: Chill Pill

description:
Boil an ally's blood, HEALING them and causing them to 
deal PYRO damage for a few turns.
name: Blood Boil

description:
Rock out with an ally, bolstering their DEFENSE and 
causing them to deal GEO damage for a few turns.
name: Rock and Roll

description:
Imbue an ally with power, causing them to deal ALL
ELEMENTAL damage, and regenerate ENERGY + SKILL.
name: Cataclysm

description:
Drop a good vibe, HEALING an ally and granting HEALTH 
regeneration.
name: Good Vibe

description:
Hit an enemy with a terrible tune, causing their 
ATTACK to drop and dealing damage every turn.
name: Bad Vibe

description:
Strike up a concert! All allies jam out, restoring
their ENERGY and restoring a portion of their HEALTH.
name: Concert

description:
Play an ear-shattering chord, destroying the ears of all
enemies. Deals damage and causes DAMAGE-OVER-TIME.
name: Discordant Chord

description:
Attack that deals KINETIC damage (MORE VS MARK)
and reduces enemy defenses. High Skill gain on hit.
name: Feint

description:
Rally up, restoring HEALTH and increasing both DEFENSE
and SKILL GAIN for a few turns.
name: Barricade Up!

description:
Slam into an enemy, dealing damage that increases with 
both ATTACK and DEFENSE (MORE VS MARK). High NRG cost.
name: Battering Ram

description:
Summon all of your energy, causing you to become
IMMUNE TO DYING for a few turns.
name: Persevere

description:
Hit an enemy's pressure point, dealing SPECIAL damage
(MORE VS MARK) and MARKing them.
name: Pressure Point

description:
A powerful blow that deals damage (MORE VS MARK),

name: Lightning Fist

description:
Throw a barrage of punches made of pure power. Deals
SPECIAL damage to multiple enemies (MORE VS MARK).
name: Thousand Punches

description:
Target an enemy's pressure point for a devastating blow. 
Deals  huge damage based on enemy Sp. Def (MORE VS MARK).
name: Essence of Exploding Heart

description:
A lamentable dirge that calls forth a wave!
Deals a wild blast of HYDRO damage to all enemies.
name: Song: Riptide

description:
A rallying tune that inspires confidence.
Grants bonuses to ATTACK and DEFENSE for party members!
name: Song: Seven Nation Army

description:
A litany not usually played by the wielder.
Restores HEALTH and ENERGY to an ally.
name: Song: Feel Good Inc.

description:
Grants Quillslayer's Boon, which increases ALL STATS,
increases CRIT CHANCE, and increases damage vs Quill.
name: Grant Quillslayer
